description: Neil Rhind will lead this historic walk along the north and east side of the Heath.

events.name: Blackheath Society Historic Walk led by Neil Rhind MBE FSA
events.notes: A guided walk over the east quartile of Blackheath, SE3.  Architectural interest covers the late 18th to early 19th century.  Lasts about 75 mins. No small children. No comfort stops. Led by Society President Neil Rhind MBE FSA. Meet on the Heath opposite No 1 Shooters Hill Road on its corner with Vanbrugh Terrace.  Ends at the Princess of Wales public house.
